### Remediation Focus (QA Check)

The previous implementation focused on structure. This test suite validates the contracts: input validation (F3) is enforced at the handler level, and all responses guarantee stable JSON regardless of outcome (F4). Specifically, tests confirm that invalid payloads result in a standardized error JSON rather than panicking or returning an HTTP 400/500 without a body.

